channel.title: Umbrella
channel.description:
Well here is an umbrella that I attempted to make. I used my 6 Point Shield for the top because Dan said it looked like an umbrella, and I added some primitive shapes to it. For the bottom, I tried using the magnet to attempt to get the curved handle, but it looked like shit so I just left it. Well here it is...
